    note right of Invisible
        setType() only valid when window is not displayable (Invisible state).
        setLocationByPlatform(true) throws IllegalComponentStateException if showing.
        createBufferStrategy() throws IllegalStateException if component not displayable.
    end note

    note right of Visible
        setType() throws IllegalComponentStateException when window is displayable.
        hide() or setVisible(false) returns window to Invisible state.
        dispose() releases native resources; window returns to Invisible (undisplayable).
    end note
